#: ../../docs/index.rst:74
msgid ""
"Or talk to us on either the `qgis-community-team "
"<https://lists.osgeo.org/mailman/listinfo/qgis-community-team>`_ mailing-"
"list, the `#qgis <https://web.libera.chat/?channels=#qgis>`_ channel on IRC "
"or the `#qgis:matrix.org <https://matrix.to/#/#qgis:osgeo.org>`_ room!"
msgstr ""
"Vagy beszéljen velünk a `qgis-community-team "
"<https://lists.osgeo.org/mailman/listinfo/qgis-community-team>`_ "
"levelezőlistán, a `#qgis <https://web.libera.chat/?channels=#qgis>`_ IRC "
"csatornán vagy a `#qgis:matrix.org <https://matrix.to/#/#qgis:osgeo.org>`_ "
"szobában."

